{"tid":1694632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息人士否認傷者即將拔喉","createTime":"2019-11-05T08:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T09:38:40.000Z","uid":125168,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"3a4cf94543de985c9dece16397d5d51623b2a6fb","tid":1694632,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:36:41.000Z","msg":"1614: 消息人士否認傷者即將拔喉。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日（4日）凌晨於將軍澳發射催淚彈驅散示威者，科技大學22歲男生其後被發現倒臥尚德邨停車場重創，兩次腦部手術仍未能控制腦水腫及出血情況。據本報兩個可靠消息渠道獲悉，科大生疑出現腦幹死亡迹象，包括瞳孔放大。其中一個消息人士表示，傷者「兩邊（瞳孔）一開始已經無乜反應」。醫管局表示，截至下午3點，科大生仍情況危殆，留醫深切治療部。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191105/s00001/1572940878754/消息-墮樓科大生疑現腦幹死亡迹象\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191105%2Fs00001%2F1572940878754%2F%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%96%91%E7%8F%BE%E8%85%A6%E5%B9%B9%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E8%BF%B9%E8%B1%A1&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=09124f4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191105%2Fs00001%2F1572940878754%2F%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%96%91%E7%8F%BE%E8%85%A6%E5%B9%B9%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E8%BF%B9%E8%B1%A1&h=b1c9df43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191105/s00001/1572940878754/消息-墮樓科大生疑現腦幹死亡迹象</a>"},{"pid":"278b580254f237cbf99709fe623501fea446ad21","tid":1694632,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"頂住呀&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"884b04ab2ce667f233ef1fbb9b49b68ed2167467","tid":1694632,"uid":24714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"dc3248a78b44cbd18912be28c947b644c5f2e11d","tid":1694632,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"頂住"},{"pid":"7dc949adcd3dc