:3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"支持住<br />\n後生細仔意志力同復完能力都強D<br />\n頂埋落去"},{"pid":"eab19b3c35ab603985f4a36169492274f18c1973","tid":1694632,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:02.000Z","msg":"東方記者去賣粉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cf11978a7bfa681329d5b9a9901dd57a62f847","tid":1694632,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:14.000Z","msg":"傷者的家屬下午3時許抵達醫院，另有一男一女市民到醫院為傷者祈禱。消息人士否認傷者即將拔喉。<br />\n<br />\n根據非牟利慈善團體香港腦科基金網頁資料，要證實傷者腦幹死亡需要兩名醫生各自進行測試，包括雙眼瞳孔是否對光線全無反應、雙側角膜反射均消失、耳朵被灌凍水後，雙眼有否左右移動等，最後才會進行窒息測試，即拔喉後病人不能自主呼吸，合共7個測試。此外，判定腦死亡，需要觀察一段時間，長短視乎導致昏迷的原因而定，但不能少於4小時。"},{"pid":"7ba21eadfabae86f40560ae168b9da74ac0abb4d","tid":1694632,"uid":143827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:17.000Z","msg":"頂住手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c285d520cfb00f1f79ca60539a1eb8c1d32c9ebd","tid":1694632,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"818dcf533411b7738f6c52cef77c03ccc3e1a138","tid":1694632,"uid":318914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:26.000Z","msg":"頂住！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4022e6c8502d7d42395ac919ab0be41d16e55b1e","tid":1694632,"uid":15968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"推，頂住🙏"},{"pid":"813be8dd349bf9fc1cae8457ccd1f017c16232a6","tid":1694632,"uid":167277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"頂住呀!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"e27138d39be97599e8e7f11a41898a13f012451e","tid":1694632,"uid":28960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"頂住呀<img src